{"tid":1683734,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"是日風向: 黑警講嘅喺事實","createTime":"2019-10-30T18:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T18:22:17.000Z","uid":275679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e6389394b7fec9c1095837953c471715d1bbc6fe","tid":1683734,"uid":275679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:19:10.000Z","msg":"幾個POST都喺度講<br />\n黑警:「嚟丫，解散我地囉。」<br />\n黑警:「好人搞革命喎。」<br />\n<br />\n然後就大量留意又話好灰、無希望、人地都喺講事實姐又退連登又乜又柒<br />\n我想講希望大家都唔好俾呢班放負撚影響到大家，我知大家而家喺好嬲，但喺如果你見到呢啲留言唔好再同佢喺度互屌，人地出呢招搞分化。<br />\n不如俾啲正能量出黎，可以試下講：「唔洗灰住，希望在明天。」<br />\n<br />\n保持良好風氣人人有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80a3028998ae4e7ca9c7b87504c5df33d0618b4","tid":1683734,"uid":275679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6897bb9d536877e12098b72d567c85ff7a06f246","tid":1683734,"uid":275679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffea388e4d4f1c55329b1f7a25acbbf38776f35","tid":1683734,"uid":275679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gi